name: Hydra 70 M151, M433 (RC Fuze)
description:
The Hydra 70 rocket is a 2.75-inch (70 mm) diameter fin-stabilized unguided rocket used primarily in the air-to-ground role.

It can be equipped with a variety of warheads, this particular version using the M151 High Explosive warhead, with an M433 time delay fuze.
